title: Truth & Consequences
description: As Marcia tries to piece together Phil and Ben’s experiences, J. Jonah Jameson challenges their account of what really happened the day Galactus fought The Fantastic Four. Starring AnnaSophia Robb as Marcia Hardesty; Seth Barrish as Phil Sheldon; Method Man as Ben Urich.
author: originals@stitcher.com (MARVELS)
